item.title: New Song- Press Start To Play
item.dc:creator: BahamutBBob
item.description:
It has some nice stuff going on, I especially liked at 1:50 where the noise cuts out to the piano, and again at 3:33 where it does the same thing.

I like how with this song, there isn’t something loud drowning out most of the subtleties for most of the song, but I’m not really a fan of the electronic “noise” (I don’t know the terms, dunno what it’s called) you used for much of the song. The stuff that kicks in at about 0:27, and then gets louder at around 1:00. That’s just personal taste, though.

Overall, it’s pretty good, but not really my style.
